<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>자동완성 실습</title>
    <style>
      .autocomplete {
        position: relative;
        display: inline-block;
      }
      
      .dropdown {
        display: none;
        position: absolute;
        top: 100%;
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        background-color: white;
        border: 1px solid #ccc;
        border-top: none;
        max-height: 200px;
        overflow-y: auto;
        z-index: 1000;
      }
      
      .dropdown-item {
        padding: 10px 15px;
        cursor: pointer;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
      }
      
      .dropdown-item:hover {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
      }
      
      .dropdown-item:last-child {
        border-bottom: none;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div
      style="
        height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
      "
    >
      <div style="margin-bottom: 15px">
        <h2>자동 완성 실습 과제</h2>
      </div>
      <div style="display: flex; margin-bottom: 30px">
        <div class="autocomplete">
          <input
            style="
              width: 400px;
              height: 35px;
              border: 1px solid rgb(182, 182, 182);
              border-radius: 10px;
              padding: 5px 10px;
            "
            id="ipt_search"
            placeholder="검색어를 입력하세요..."
          />
          <div class="dropdown" id="dropdown"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        id="result-display"
        style="
          width: 500px;
          min-height: 500px;
          padding: 10px;
          margin-top: 20px;
          font-size: 14px;
          white-space: pre-line;
        "
      >
        검색 결과가 여기에 표시됩니다
      </div>
    </div>
    <script type="text/javascript" src="/js/autocomplete/uiControl.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
